@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5255
@accessToken = paste_jwt_after_login

### Login (demo — trả JWT)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "any"
}

###

### Cần JWT (dán token từ login vào biến @accessToken hoặc thay trực tiếp)
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/appusers
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/appinfo
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/appusers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "email": "demo2@example.com",
  "displayName": "Demo User 2"
}

###
